metadata.name: Vishnu - The Omnipotent Creator
metadata.description:
In this Web3 world, where every creator is hustling and paving their own path to be the best, there's only one creator who we can't surpass! 
Lord Vishnu, a princely and benevolent being, the originator and creator of this universe and the one who rules over the cosmos is a true epitome of a successful creator who succeeded in creating the most beautiful art in the galaxy and that is this perfect world of ours which we call as EARTH!
As sacred as he is, so are we, so is his creation, so are our lives and the stories and art we create each day!
